<ul><li><i><b><a href="/wiki/Folklore_(Taylor_Swift_album)" title="Folklore (Taylor Swift album)">Folklore</a></b></i> by <a href="/wiki/Taylor_Swift" title="Taylor Swift">Taylor Swift</a> wins <a href="/wiki/Grammy_Award_for_Album_of_the_Year" title="Grammy Award for Album of the Year">Album of the Year</a> and <a href="/wiki/Billie_Eilish" title="Billie Eilish">Billie Eilish</a>'s  <i>(pictured)</i> "<b><a href="/wiki/Everything_I_Wanted" title="Everything I Wanted">Everything I Wanted</a></b>" wins <a href="/wiki/Grammy_Award_for_Record_of_the_Year" title="Grammy Award for Record of the Year">Record of the Year</a> at <b><a href="/wiki/63rd_Annual_Grammy_Awards" title="63rd Annual Grammy Awards">the Grammy Awards</a></b>.</li>
